#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.maximum.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.maximum"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:1 of
msgid "Element-wise maximum of tensor elements."
msgstr "逐元素计算张量元素的最大值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:3 of
msgid ""
"Compare two tensors and returns a new array containing the element-wise "
"maxima. If one of the elements being compared is a NaN, then that element"
" is returned. If both elements are NaNs then the first is returned. The "
"latter distinction is important for complex NaNs, which are defined as at"
" least one of the real or imaginary parts being a NaN. The net effect is "
"that NaNs are propagated."
msgstr ""
"比较两个张量并返回一个包含逐元素最大值的新数组。如果被比较的元素中有一个"
"是 NaN，则返回该元素。如果两个元素都是 NaN，则返回第一个元素。后一个区别"
"对于复数 NaN 很重要，复数 NaN 被定义为实部或虚部中至少有一个是 NaN。最终"
"的效果是 NaN 会被传播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:10
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:13 of
msgid ""
"The tensors holding the elements to be compared. They must have the same "
"shape, or shapes that can be broadcast to a single shape."
msgstr "包含待比较元素的张量。它们必须具有相同的形状，或可以广播为相同形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:16 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，它必须具有可以广播输入的形状。如果"
"未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的"
"长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:21 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:26 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The maximum of `x1` and `x2`, element-wise.  Returns scalar if "
"both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- `x1` 和 `x2` 的逐元素最大值。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回"
"标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`minimum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:33 of
msgid "Element-wise minimum of two tensors, propagates NaNs."
msgstr "两个张量的逐元素最小值，传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:36 of
msgid "Element-wise maximum of two tensors, ignores NaNs."
msgstr "两个张量的逐元素最大值，忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`amax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:39 of
msgid "The maximum value of a tensor along a given axis, propagates NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的张量最大值，传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`nanmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:42 of
msgid "The maximum value of a tensor along a given axis, ignores NaNs."
msgstr "沿给定轴的张量最大值，忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fmin`, :py:obj:`amin`, :py:obj:`nanmin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:47 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.maximum.maximum:48 of
msgid ""
"The maximum is equivalent to ``mt.where(x1 >= x2, x1, x2)`` when neither "
"x1 nor x2 are nans, but it is faster and does proper broadcasting."
msgstr ""
"当 x1 和 x2 都不是 NaN 时，最大值等价于 ``mt.where(x1 >= x2, x1, x2)``，"
"但它更快并且正确地进行广播。"

